:{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31842,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/waki-zakat-al-fitr-sujud-sahw\/","url_meta":{"origin":31942,"position":2},"title":"Waki\u2019 on Ramadan: Zakat al-Fitr like prostration of forgetfulness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nawawi reported: Waki\u2019 ibn al-Jarrah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cZakat al-Fitr is to the month of Ramadan like the prostration of forgetfulness is to prayer. It makes up for deficiencies in fasting just as the prostration makes up for deficiencies in prayer.\u201d Source: al-Majmu\u0304\u2019 Sharh\u0323 al-Muhadhab 6\/140\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33845,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/12\/22\/ayat-al-kursi-protection-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":31942,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ayat al-Kursi: Verse of Throne for protection from Satan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, entrusted me to protect the charity of Ramadan. Someone came to me and began taking from the food. I took hold of him, and I said, \u201cI will certainly take you to the Messenger of Allah!\u201d Abu\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18566,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/17\/zakat-food-clothing-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":31942,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Zakat: If he gives food, clothing, or prayer in charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen a man earns wealth from what is lawful and he feeds himself, or clothes another among the creation of Allah, it will be regarded as charity for him. When a Muslim man is without\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18055,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/05\/zakat-allah-withholds-rain\/","url_meta":{"origin":31942,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Zakat: Rain held back if people withhold charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNever do people withhold alms from their wealth but that a portion from the sky will be held back; were it not for the animals, it would never rain.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 13454 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/w